        <num>CHC 1279.3</num>
        <heading>1279.3.  Purpose</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1279.3.  Purpose
Notwithstanding any provision of the law to the contrary, in order to facilitate the recruitment of new families for children, the incentives provided in this Chapter shall be made available for those children who have been adopted from the custody of the state and meet eligibility requirements.</p>
        </content>
